## Telegram Bot

Bot zayavkalar uchun ishchi guruhga xabar yuboradi.

### Bot holatlari

```
Yangi zayavka
     в†“
[рџ“ћ Men olaman]  в†ђ birinchi bosgan ishchi oladi
     в†“
[вњ… Tasdiqlandi]  [вќЊ Bekor qilindi]
```

### Bot komandalar

- `/list` вЂ” zayavkalar ro'yxatini ko'rish
  - рџ†• Gaplashilmaganlar
  - вњ… Tasdiqlananlar
  - вќЊ Bekor qilinganlar

### Guruhga ulash

1. Botni guruhga qo'shing
2. Guruhda `/start` yuboring
3. `https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates` dan guruh chat id ni oling
4. `.env.docker` da `TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID` ni yangilang

---

## Docker komandalar

```bash
# Ishga tushirish
docker-compose up -d

# To'xtatish
docker-compose down

# Loglar
docker-compose logs web
docker-compose logs bot

# Restart
docker-compose restart web
docker-compose restart bot

# Shell
docker-compose exec web python manage.py shell
```

